WEBVTT

00:56.097 --> 00:59.225
EPISODE 12

00:59.601 --> 01:00.685
Come on in.

01:02.937 --> 01:04.230
I brought some tea.

01:06.191 --> 01:07.776
Thank you. Could you brew some for us?

01:10.236 --> 01:11.237
Over here.

01:12.614 --> 01:13.740
- Have a seat.
- Thank you.

01:19.120 --> 01:22.457
I know the request was out of the blue,
so I appreciate you agreeing to it.

01:24.167 --> 01:26.002
There's no need to feel that way.

01:26.086 --> 01:28.296
I'm just sorry if asking you here
was an inconvenience.

01:28.546 --> 01:29.547
Not at all.

01:32.842 --> 01:34.094
To see you here

01:35.011 --> 01:38.223
makes me wish again
that I had met you sooner.

01:40.058 --> 01:43.269
Please don't worry about that.
It's all in the past.

01:47.398 --> 01:49.275
The past? Is that how it'll be?

01:51.778 --> 01:56.407
I still feel the same way as I did before.

01:59.869 --> 02:02.956
I'm not one to be taken aback that easily,

02:04.415 --> 02:05.500
but you always manage to do so.

02:09.045 --> 02:11.089
Why did you want to see me today then?

02:12.966 --> 02:16.177
I was hoping you'd disapprove
of me even stronger.

02:21.850 --> 02:23.643
Your cab will be here soon.

02:23.726 --> 02:27.147
My cab? That's not what's important here.

02:27.605 --> 02:30.400
Your marriage.
Keep your eyes on the prize.

02:31.109 --> 02:33.444
Aren't the stars aligning?

02:34.028 --> 02:36.406
It's not just me who's fond of you.

02:36.489 --> 02:40.910
Your father is quite satisfied
with my daughter, too.

02:42.495 --> 02:44.622
Could it be any better?

02:46.040 --> 02:47.083
- Gi-seok.
- Yes.

02:47.167 --> 02:49.836
- Gi-seok.
- Yes, sir.

02:50.378 --> 02:53.381
You have always been my second son-in-law.

02:53.590 --> 02:55.800
I knew it since
the first time I saw you.

02:57.719 --> 02:58.636
Thank you.

03:00.805 --> 03:02.182
I'm the one who's grateful.

03:02.265 --> 03:05.310
How can I not be
when I'm gaining a son-in-law like you?

03:06.394 --> 03:09.272
Don't you worry about a thing.

03:09.731 --> 03:11.816
I'll clear the path for you.

03:15.153 --> 03:16.613
So in other words,

03:18.531 --> 03:21.284
it's to make your father give up.

03:22.660 --> 03:25.997
My father can't seem
to give up on Gi-seok.

03:27.999 --> 03:30.919
My parents' opinions do matter,

03:31.961 --> 03:36.007
but what I want should come first
when it comes to my personal life.

03:38.009 --> 03:40.845
That's why I came here
despite it being disrespectful.

03:41.304 --> 03:42.472
I see no disrespect.

03:43.264 --> 03:44.933
Humans are all selfish beings anyway.

03:47.769 --> 03:49.187
In that case though,

03:50.647 --> 03:53.983
I can't let someone
purposely break my son's heart.

03:56.819 --> 04:02.367
There is no future for me and Gi-seok.
I don't want there to be one.

04:05.662 --> 04:07.121
Because there's someone else?

04:11.125 --> 04:12.710
I won't hold it against you.

04:14.003 --> 04:18.841
Still,
you never know what'll happen, right?

04:19.175 --> 04:21.886
I advise you
not to make any rash decisions.

04:25.390 --> 04:27.350
I don't care about the frivolous things

04:27.934 --> 04:30.061
and am a man of patience.

04:30.812 --> 04:33.064
That's why
I fully understand your position

04:34.440 --> 04:36.693
and can give you all the time you need.

04:39.821 --> 04:43.783
You know that I no longer
have feelings for Gi-seok.

04:44.242 --> 04:46.369
No one's sure of their feelings.

04:47.078 --> 04:48.538
They can always change.

04:49.706 --> 04:51.833
I may be like this now, but who knows?

04:52.542 --> 04:54.335
Just like you said earlier,

04:55.420 --> 04:57.380
I might disapprove of you even stronger.

06:30.098 --> 06:31.974
I'm too exhausted,
so I'll be hitting the sack.

06:32.350 --> 06:33.518
I'll talk to you tomorrow.

07:24.652 --> 07:25.653
My gosh.

07:29.323 --> 07:30.408
What brings you by?

07:31.284 --> 07:33.828
Your father wanted me to deliver this.

07:35.455 --> 07:36.372
What is it?

07:36.956 --> 07:39.000
It's not like I'd know.

07:40.084 --> 07:41.169
Anyway, I'll see you around.

07:41.961 --> 07:42.962
Sure.

07:43.838 --> 07:44.881
Take care.

08:26.172 --> 08:27.590
What would you like for lunch?

08:28.799 --> 08:29.926
Didn't anyone call?

08:30.426 --> 08:33.179
I didn't hear a ring.
Should I get your phone?

08:33.679 --> 08:36.766
It's fine.
As for lunch, let's keep it light.

08:37.016 --> 08:38.017
Yes, sir.

08:58.829 --> 08:59.872
- Here.
- Right.

09:01.499 --> 09:03.626
Did Jeong-in say anything?

09:04.335 --> 09:05.795
Didn't Gi-seok meet her father?

09:06.254 --> 09:07.922
Is it already over between you two?

09:08.506 --> 09:09.632
Give me back my shoes.

09:10.883 --> 09:11.717
I'm off.

09:11.801 --> 09:13.427
- Don't miss it next week.
- See you.

09:13.511 --> 09:14.595
- Right.
- Bye.

09:38.286 --> 09:39.370
Hi, Ji-ho.

09:40.413 --> 09:41.581
Did I wake you?

09:42.665 --> 09:43.666
No.

09:44.292 --> 09:45.501
What were you up to?

09:46.377 --> 09:47.587
Thinking about causing trouble.

09:48.754 --> 09:49.964
You already did that yesterday.

09:52.842 --> 09:53.968
So you really did.

09:54.719 --> 09:55.845
Where were you yesterday?

09:58.723 --> 09:59.890
I'd rather not say.

10:01.934 --> 10:03.102
Then don't.

10:04.979 --> 10:07.481
I'm not trying
to keep it a secret or anything.

10:08.816 --> 10:10.401
It'll do no one good,

10:10.484 --> 10:11.736
so I don't want to say it.

10:14.697 --> 10:15.698
Got it.

10:19.243 --> 10:20.411
You're at it again.

10:21.495 --> 10:22.788
Only you seem mature.

10:23.873 --> 10:25.499
Even though I try not to be,

10:26.000 --> 10:28.669
I keep getting anxious
because I'm too impatient.

10:29.670 --> 10:31.213
Maybe I haven't given you certainty.

10:34.383 --> 10:35.801
Would you like to meet my parents?

10:38.554 --> 10:39.930
If only I could see your reaction.

10:42.516 --> 10:43.684
I'm unfazed.

10:46.020 --> 10:47.063
As if.

10:49.231 --> 10:52.151
What if they're not fond of me?

10:54.362 --> 10:55.571
Then we'll have to break up.

10:55.655 --> 10:57.907
- Hey!
- "Hey"?

11:00.993 --> 11:02.453
You know I didn't mean it like that.

11:03.621 --> 11:05.373
I meant it in an endearing way.

11:08.167 --> 11:09.377
You and your excuses.

11:10.961 --> 11:12.380
I'm really worried, though.

11:15.049 --> 11:17.301
My parents are nice people

11:17.718 --> 11:20.012
and will know that you are, too.

11:21.389 --> 11:22.765
I'm jealous of you.

11:24.809 --> 11:28.896
Looking at you, I can tell
that your parents are nice people, too.

11:30.272 --> 11:31.482
But you already met my dad.

11:33.484 --> 11:35.653
All parents get greedy
when it comes to their kids.

11:36.737 --> 11:38.739
I somewhat understand
where he's coming from.

11:40.574 --> 11:42.076
I hear that Jae-in gave you advice.

11:43.953 --> 11:45.329
I've already been bracing myself.

11:47.623 --> 11:49.583
Besides, I'm too happy right now

11:50.501 --> 11:52.044
to rush into anything in a hurry.

11:54.046 --> 11:55.756
I even think that

11:56.757 --> 11:57.758
this is more than enough.

11:59.427 --> 12:00.469
Not me.

12:02.847 --> 12:05.266
I want you badly.

12:11.605 --> 12:12.773
What a sweet life.

12:20.364 --> 12:21.866
Why didn't you call in advance?

12:22.700 --> 12:23.826
- Have a seat.
- Right.

12:26.495 --> 12:29.206
- Where's Seo-in?
- She's home.

12:29.540 --> 12:31.083
Why didn't you come together?

12:31.751 --> 12:32.835
Well...

12:35.671 --> 12:38.299
Honey, we have a guest,
so don't just stand there.

12:38.507 --> 12:39.633
Get him something to drink.

12:40.259 --> 12:42.136
What do you want? What do you need?

12:42.219 --> 12:43.345
It's fine, Mother.

12:44.054 --> 12:45.014
What...

12:47.725 --> 12:48.976
Unbelievable.

12:53.564 --> 12:55.483
Si-hoon, what are you doing?

12:56.275 --> 12:57.318
I'm sorry.

12:58.235 --> 12:59.820
It's all my fault.

13:00.529 --> 13:01.530
What do you mean?

13:02.239 --> 13:04.366
Honey, why is he acting this way?

13:04.450 --> 13:07.369
- Honey, actually--
- I won't divorce Seo-in.

13:09.079 --> 13:10.164
A divorce?

13:10.247 --> 13:13.125
All I wanted was to give her a good life,

13:13.209 --> 13:15.628
but it didn't go as I wanted.

13:15.711 --> 13:18.130
That's why I acted like a complete fool.

13:19.590 --> 13:23.052
I must've been stressed out
about moving the clinic.

13:23.135 --> 13:25.763
I wasn't as attentive as I could be

13:26.847 --> 13:29.016
- and lashed out at her for no reason.
- Excuse me.

13:29.934 --> 13:32.144
Did I hear you correctly?
Is that all you did?

13:33.103 --> 13:34.146
So?

13:35.022 --> 13:36.565
Is she now demanding a divorce?

13:36.649 --> 13:39.151
- Honey, listen to me--
- I was wasted that day.

13:39.235 --> 13:41.779
The argument got heated,
and I ended up hitting her.

13:43.447 --> 13:44.657
You hit her?

13:44.740 --> 13:47.117
I really shouldn't have, but I did.

13:47.993 --> 13:50.120
I was completely wasted that day.

13:51.080 --> 13:51.956
Father, Mother,

13:53.332 --> 13:54.834
please forgive me this once.

14:00.548 --> 14:01.882
I won't complain

14:03.133 --> 14:06.387
even if you decide
to beat me to a pulp right now,

14:06.470 --> 14:08.222
so please stop this divorce.

14:08.305 --> 14:10.766
I can't live without Seo-in.

14:13.352 --> 14:14.436
I...

14:15.729 --> 14:16.856
I'll stay by her side

14:17.815 --> 14:21.193
and not mistreat her ever again,

14:21.277 --> 14:22.361
so, please...

14:24.029 --> 14:26.615
So please help me this once.

14:26.699 --> 14:29.660
I can't live without her. Please.

14:35.291 --> 14:38.335
Father, please forgive me.
I'm truly sorry.

14:39.420 --> 14:40.421
Stand up.

14:42.298 --> 14:43.757
Stand up!

14:47.428 --> 14:48.345
Lead the way.

14:49.346 --> 14:51.974
- Head home.
- Why would you go there?

14:52.057 --> 14:53.684
A divorce is just absurd!

15:03.444 --> 15:04.278
What?

15:05.696 --> 15:06.947
You're annoying, that's why.

15:07.573 --> 15:10.117
Is that something to say
to a friend who came by on a day off?

15:10.284 --> 15:12.453
Don't you think I know
you're just stopping by

15:12.536 --> 15:15.080
even though you want to head up
straight to the third floor?

15:15.873 --> 15:17.207
Nothing gets past you.

15:17.708 --> 15:19.084
Aren't I decent, though?

15:19.418 --> 15:20.544
I'm meeting him tonight,

15:20.628 --> 15:22.129
but I came by to see you early.

15:22.755 --> 15:25.049
- Why are you outside though?
- There's nothing to eat.

15:25.215 --> 15:27.593
I figured we could
grab something to eat outside.

15:27.676 --> 15:29.094
I see. I'll buy then.

15:29.345 --> 15:31.180
Of course, you should. Thanks in advance.

15:33.265 --> 15:34.767
Ms. Lee!

15:35.601 --> 15:36.644
Hi, Eun-u.

15:38.228 --> 15:39.396
Have you been well?

15:43.192 --> 15:44.693
How do you know Eun-u?

15:46.779 --> 15:50.282
It's nice to meet you. I'm Lee Jeong-in.

15:51.033 --> 15:52.159
I see.

15:53.661 --> 15:54.578
Well,

15:56.121 --> 15:59.124
- Ji-ho and I--
- The library...

15:59.708 --> 16:00.876
Yes, that's right.

16:01.543 --> 16:04.129
I'm a librarian.

16:04.213 --> 16:05.089
I see.

16:05.839 --> 16:06.966
Well, what brings you here...

16:07.633 --> 16:09.510
I'm her friend,

16:09.593 --> 16:12.304
and I coincidentally happen to live
on the second floor.

16:12.388 --> 16:13.597
I see.

16:14.098 --> 16:15.641
Grandma, let's go.

16:17.977 --> 16:19.103
Bye then.

16:20.312 --> 16:21.271
Bye.

16:38.831 --> 16:40.040
There you go.

16:40.416 --> 16:42.042
- I'll take that.
- Sure.

16:48.132 --> 16:49.967
Why isn't Ms. Lee coming?

16:51.802 --> 16:52.803
Why do you suddenly ask?

16:53.470 --> 16:54.763
We ran into her outside.

16:55.973 --> 16:57.891
She's a librarian, so I hear.

17:00.352 --> 17:02.896
Did you see her? Did you meet Ms. Lee?

17:06.775 --> 17:09.528
"Eun-u, have you been well?"
That's what she said.

17:10.904 --> 17:12.031
Even I was surprised.

17:12.740 --> 17:14.241
Who knew that I'd meet her here?

17:15.534 --> 17:17.494
Her friend lives downstairs.

17:17.911 --> 17:20.414
I heard that, too.
She said it's a coincidence.

17:21.457 --> 17:23.876
It is. Even I was surprised
when I found out.

17:26.837 --> 17:29.173
- Mom.
- I didn't say anything,

17:29.757 --> 17:32.426
so stop acting like
you got caught doing something bad.

17:33.802 --> 17:35.471
I was going to introduce her to you.

17:36.138 --> 17:38.640
- What did you think of her?
- The meeting was brief.

17:39.349 --> 17:40.350
Still.

17:42.186 --> 17:43.937
Maybe it was too brief,

17:44.646 --> 17:48.025
but she did seem smart and meticulous.
She's pretty, too.

17:53.405 --> 17:54.740
Oh, I should sort these out.

17:59.036 --> 18:01.413
Gosh, I look depressing today.

18:02.289 --> 18:03.624
I should've put on some makeup.

18:04.249 --> 18:06.877
There's only so much makeup can do
to hide our flaws at our age.

18:10.672 --> 18:12.758
I'm thinking that I should move.

18:12.841 --> 18:15.427
I'm done getting caught up
in your messes.

18:15.969 --> 18:18.097
I wouldn't have met Ji-ho
if you hadn't lived there.

18:19.223 --> 18:21.225
Are you going to blame me
if things go wrong?

18:21.308 --> 18:22.851
I'm saying you'll be rewarded someday.

18:24.937 --> 18:28.524
What do you think
Ji-ho's mom thought of me?

18:29.316 --> 18:30.359
Did I come off rude?

18:31.485 --> 18:34.196
What's on your mind, though?
Are you even thinking at all?

18:34.488 --> 18:35.531
What now?

18:36.573 --> 18:37.616
That boy...

18:38.325 --> 18:40.202
Eun-u, was it?

18:41.203 --> 18:42.746
Are you sure you can be a mother?

18:44.164 --> 18:46.792
This again?
I'm not saying it'll happen soon.

18:48.794 --> 18:51.922
Are you just dating Ji-ho then?
Are you keeping your options open?

18:54.424 --> 18:57.886
Do you also believe that
feelings always change?

18:58.804 --> 18:59.888
Well...

19:00.722 --> 19:02.099
You're living proof of it.

19:02.766 --> 19:04.351
Why did you break up with Gi-seok?

19:05.060 --> 19:06.770
- Here's your dish.
- Thank you.

19:13.277 --> 19:15.195
You can add in some sauce if you like.

19:15.279 --> 19:16.738
- Please enjoy.
- Thank you.

19:22.870 --> 19:25.205
A person never changes.

19:26.123 --> 19:28.709
Feelings can shift depending
on the moment,

19:28.876 --> 19:30.460
but not human nature.

19:37.384 --> 19:38.510
It's Gi-seok.

19:39.344 --> 19:40.387
See?

19:40.721 --> 19:43.056
People never change. They never do.

19:48.270 --> 19:49.146
What?

19:49.813 --> 19:52.024
I'd like to talk. Are you at the library?

19:54.776 --> 19:56.069
I'll go to where you are.

19:59.156 --> 20:00.324
I want to talk.

20:03.202 --> 20:05.579
Then I'll wait at your house
until you come home.

20:11.084 --> 20:15.714
Married life doesn't always go as planned.

20:16.298 --> 20:19.384
How can you call it a marriage
when you bring up divorce all the time?

20:20.344 --> 20:23.889
Being patient and understanding
is how you mature as a couple.

20:24.264 --> 20:26.475
You can't act on your feelings
every single time.

20:27.726 --> 20:31.438
Your mom and I also
endured all the difficulties

20:31.521 --> 20:32.648
and that's how we got here.

20:37.653 --> 20:42.199
What should I do?
Should I beat him up in front of you?

20:44.451 --> 20:46.161
Will you forgive him then?

20:48.997 --> 20:51.625
I knew how this would affect my life,
but I still made this decision.

20:52.876 --> 20:54.878
Do not think that it was out of anger.

20:55.170 --> 20:57.339
I never said it was a rash decision.

20:58.507 --> 21:01.468
I'd love nothing more
than to beat the daylights out of him.

21:03.512 --> 21:05.222
I don't care if you were drunk.

21:06.139 --> 21:08.058
How could you make such a mistake?

21:10.477 --> 21:11.520
I'm sorry.

21:13.647 --> 21:16.733
Did he tell you
that it was a drunken mistake?

21:17.985 --> 21:19.111
Of course, it was a mistake.

21:20.153 --> 21:23.407
He wouldn't have done it on purpose.
You're unbelievable.

21:29.496 --> 21:30.497
Say what you want.

21:31.039 --> 21:32.749
I'm getting a divorce.

21:32.833 --> 21:34.584
Sure. Divorce is the easy route.

21:35.168 --> 21:38.130
However, you're not like most couples.

21:39.423 --> 21:42.551
Especially you can kiss
your good girl image goodbye.

21:43.802 --> 21:44.928
Must I say that myself?

21:46.596 --> 21:48.140
Forgive him this once.

21:48.974 --> 21:52.519
After you get back on track,
you might get pregnant and--

21:52.602 --> 21:53.603
I'm already pregnant.

21:58.525 --> 22:01.361
I'm pregnant,
which is why I must divorce him.

22:02.654 --> 22:05.365
I can't raise this baby
with him in the picture.

22:05.449 --> 22:07.576
- Seo-in...
- You listen to me.

22:08.785 --> 22:11.330
This is my baby.
It has nothing to do with you.

22:12.289 --> 22:14.374
- Honey.
- Seo-in,

22:15.667 --> 22:18.211
you should've told us about this sooner.

22:18.295 --> 22:20.088
Divorce isn't an option in this situation.

22:20.547 --> 22:21.381
My goodness.

22:22.174 --> 22:24.176
How can you be this immature and reckless?

22:24.259 --> 22:25.886
Your daughter was assaulted!

22:26.636 --> 22:27.888
How can you be this way?

22:29.681 --> 22:31.641
Aren't you hurt by this at all?

22:32.684 --> 22:34.978
Shouldn't your heart be ripped
into pieces?

22:36.730 --> 22:38.440
How can you be so cruel?

22:40.317 --> 22:42.402
What have I done that is so wrong?

22:42.986 --> 22:45.864
How much more must I endure
for you to understand me?

22:45.947 --> 22:47.699
Seo-in, please.

22:47.783 --> 22:49.409
Mom, I...

22:49.493 --> 22:51.536
It's all right.

23:18.522 --> 23:19.940
I mostly...

23:21.024 --> 23:22.025
want to apologize to you.

23:24.736 --> 23:26.113
Just look at your father.

23:28.198 --> 23:30.242
I'm the one who should apologize to you.

23:33.245 --> 23:35.080
It wasn't like I got my hopes up.

23:36.540 --> 23:37.791
Still, how could he...

23:41.336 --> 23:44.548
How could I have lived
with a man like that all these years?

23:46.049 --> 23:47.676
It's pathetic.

23:49.219 --> 23:50.387
It's humiliating.

24:10.240 --> 24:13.660
I'd like to talk to Seo-in for a moment.

24:14.327 --> 24:15.412
About what?

24:15.996 --> 24:18.081
Shouldn't you be too mortified
to even open your mouth?

24:20.709 --> 24:21.710
Mom, leave it.

24:24.880 --> 24:25.881
It's all right.

24:56.578 --> 24:57.871
I'm sorry.

24:59.122 --> 25:00.457
It's all my fault.

25:00.999 --> 25:02.292
I'm a bastard.

25:05.253 --> 25:09.007
I'll devote my life to you and our baby
for the rest of my life.

25:09.090 --> 25:10.550
So please forgive me this once.

25:12.636 --> 25:14.221
You think you hit the jackpot, don't you?

25:15.472 --> 25:16.723
I'm pregnant now,

25:17.057 --> 25:18.850
so you think I'm out of options.

25:19.976 --> 25:21.311
Seo-in, please.

25:23.980 --> 25:28.068
I'll file for divorce right away.
I have enough evidence.

25:31.738 --> 25:33.990
It won't just ruin me, though.

25:36.243 --> 25:38.495
Revealing that you're a son of a bitch

25:39.746 --> 25:41.498
will also let people know

25:41.748 --> 25:44.584
that I'm a pathetic woman
who only married for money.

25:48.088 --> 25:49.464
Just this once.

25:50.131 --> 25:52.217
Can't you overlook it just this once?

25:52.467 --> 25:54.302
This won't happen again. I promise.

25:54.386 --> 25:58.974
If I ever hurt you in any way again,

25:59.057 --> 26:01.017
be it even a single word,

26:02.102 --> 26:04.145
I'll be the first to suggest
that we get a divorce.

26:04.229 --> 26:05.814
I'll leave you be.

26:06.940 --> 26:08.024
Please?

26:08.733 --> 26:09.985
Give up your paternal rights.

26:10.819 --> 26:12.529
Then I won't press assault charges.

26:15.407 --> 26:17.450
Either that or live
as an ex-con your whole life.

26:21.705 --> 26:22.956
I already asked you this,

26:24.457 --> 26:26.334
but must you go this far?

26:26.710 --> 26:28.670
Thank the baby for my leniency.

26:44.978 --> 26:46.855
Then I choose to be an ex-con.

26:50.400 --> 26:52.319
How can I give up my paternal rights?

26:54.529 --> 26:55.697
I am the father, after all.

27:22.849 --> 27:23.975
Is he already asleep?

27:24.601 --> 27:26.227
Well, it's past his nap time.

27:26.895 --> 27:28.146
It's okay. I'll do it later.

27:28.563 --> 27:29.939
Don't let the laundry pile up.

27:30.357 --> 27:32.692
It's quite warm these days,
so it'll stink quickly.

27:34.819 --> 27:37.238
I guess you liked Jeong-in.

27:41.201 --> 27:43.286
I just don't want your place to stink.

27:43.370 --> 27:45.747
Where's that coming from?

27:48.124 --> 27:49.125
Goodness.

27:54.631 --> 27:56.091
I'll be right back.

27:56.341 --> 27:57.258
What?

28:16.486 --> 28:17.696
I didn't expect you here.

28:18.446 --> 28:20.657
I ran into your mother.

28:21.574 --> 28:22.659
I heard.

28:22.992 --> 28:25.453
What did she say?
Did she say anything about me?

28:26.496 --> 28:28.873
- She said you're pretty.
- Be honest.

28:29.374 --> 28:31.960
Actually, she said you're ugly.

28:33.670 --> 28:35.839
- Goodness, you actually look ugly now.
- What?

28:37.090 --> 28:39.050
- Do you like that I'm ugly?
- You're a hard puncher.

28:40.260 --> 28:42.262
Good for you. You have an ugly girlfriend.

28:42.804 --> 28:44.472
- Go away.
- That tickles.

28:45.890 --> 28:46.933
That really tickles.

28:47.684 --> 28:49.144
- Why you!
- Okay, fine.

28:55.316 --> 28:56.985
You were aiming for a headbutt,
weren't you?

28:57.444 --> 28:59.696
You're much taller,
so I have to jump this much.

29:12.625 --> 29:13.710
I said it's fine.

29:18.798 --> 29:20.300
How can you be fine with it?

29:20.884 --> 29:21.968
You should be upset.

29:23.261 --> 29:24.679
I would be upset if you hid it

29:25.054 --> 29:26.973
or met him but lied to me about it.

29:27.599 --> 29:30.518
Also, seeing that your father hasn't
said much even after meeting Gi-seok,

29:30.602 --> 29:32.145
I'm thinking he probably tried his best.

29:33.688 --> 29:36.733
He may still not deserve a compliment,
but you can at least listen.

29:38.902 --> 29:41.988
In the past, you talked as if
you'd never see Gi-seok again.

29:43.448 --> 29:44.532
This I can let go.

29:45.950 --> 29:47.285
Now, you're all lenient.

29:48.328 --> 29:49.621
Are you just incredibly patient?

29:50.330 --> 29:51.748
Or are you full of confidence?

29:53.166 --> 29:54.334
I trust you. That's all.

29:56.503 --> 29:58.421
They say that feelings change.

29:59.547 --> 30:00.799
And I've experienced that.

30:02.675 --> 30:04.344
It didn't happen because you met me.

30:06.179 --> 30:07.388
Now, you're being arrogant.

30:08.139 --> 30:10.016
Everyone needs this kind of arrogance.

30:15.104 --> 30:16.314
- What was that about?
- Nothing.

30:38.044 --> 30:39.170
Why did you bring me here?

30:40.964 --> 30:42.382
It's been so long, hasn't it?

30:44.884 --> 30:46.177
Are we meeting your father?

30:48.012 --> 30:49.138
Or my dad?

30:51.850 --> 30:53.810
I didn't think of that.

30:56.938 --> 30:57.897
Let's get out.

31:37.186 --> 31:38.605
This is where we first met.

31:41.399 --> 31:42.483
You remember, right?

31:51.868 --> 31:53.953
You were with your father.
The moment I saw you,

31:56.789 --> 31:58.082
I was totally smitten by you.

32:01.920 --> 32:03.129
I hesitated for a few days,

32:04.797 --> 32:06.424
then pestered him to introduce me to you.

32:08.676 --> 32:09.928
That was already four years ago.

32:19.646 --> 32:20.605
I know I took too long.

32:37.705 --> 32:38.706
It's what you think it is.

32:41.417 --> 32:42.543
Let's get married.

32:47.674 --> 32:49.133
What you think doesn't matter.

32:51.219 --> 32:52.637
I'm choosing this for your sake.

33:38.099 --> 33:40.309
There you go. Done!

34:48.920 --> 34:50.838
I saw the girl Ji-ho told us about.

34:51.380 --> 34:53.007
- Where?
- In front of his place.

34:53.508 --> 34:55.093
Her friend lives in the same building.

34:56.844 --> 35:00.181
They were already holding hands.

35:00.640 --> 35:03.267
He seemed so happy to see her.

35:05.061 --> 35:08.147
I didn't know my son
could look that happy and excited.

35:09.398 --> 35:11.526
- She's pretty, isn't she?
- Yes, she is.

35:16.447 --> 35:17.490
Wait, how do you know?

35:18.825 --> 35:20.785
All women are pretty when they're young.

35:21.452 --> 35:24.455
You were absolutely gorgeous
back in the day. Eun-u!

35:25.498 --> 35:26.707
Let's have some fruit.

35:28.167 --> 35:29.460
Go tell your dad to join us.

35:53.109 --> 35:55.653
Why are you sulking?

35:57.989 --> 35:59.657
Even just hearing about
a complete stranger

36:00.283 --> 36:02.618
going through what Seo-in experienced

36:02.869 --> 36:05.121
should make you shake with rage.

36:06.581 --> 36:08.916
Do you realize
how much you disappointed me today?

36:09.834 --> 36:11.419
How could you be so despicable?

36:11.502 --> 36:12.879
Give me a break.

36:13.421 --> 36:15.131
She's pregnant with his child.

36:15.214 --> 36:17.008
Should I have encouraged her
to get a divorce?

36:17.258 --> 36:20.720
You went there to tell her
that divorce is simply not an option.

36:22.054 --> 36:23.598
Your daughter was hit by her husband.

36:25.641 --> 36:27.810
She's a victim of domestic violence,

36:28.144 --> 36:29.729
but you want her to bury it

36:29.812 --> 36:32.523
because you don't want people to find out.
I can read you like a book.

36:33.816 --> 36:35.318
Divorce is nothing to be ashamed of.

36:37.486 --> 36:39.822
You should be ashamed
that you're a shallow-minded father

36:39.906 --> 36:41.824
who's more concerned
with what other people think.

36:50.625 --> 36:52.168
Let's hurry Jeong-in's wedding.

36:54.503 --> 36:56.005
Who knows what will happen with Seo-in?

36:57.215 --> 37:00.176
No family would want a daughter-in-law
with a divorced sister.

37:01.093 --> 37:02.929
We should marry her off
before that happens.

37:03.638 --> 37:04.639
Hey.

37:06.724 --> 37:07.808
Lee Tae-hak.

37:09.143 --> 37:11.270
Do you even have a heart?

37:21.405 --> 37:23.157
Why did you even receive this?

37:25.993 --> 37:27.828
He said I can keep it or throw it out

37:28.496 --> 37:29.914
because he bought it for me.

37:31.165 --> 37:32.833
And you fell for that old-school trick?

37:33.751 --> 37:35.253
You should've thrown it in his face.

37:36.629 --> 37:37.964
I obviously thought of doing that.

37:40.883 --> 37:43.928
But it's not like we're enemies.
There's no reason to be that mean to him.

37:45.972 --> 37:48.015
Do you still have feelings left
for Gi-seok?

37:53.896 --> 37:55.064
It just felt so futile.

37:57.441 --> 37:58.609
I was surprised to realize

37:59.527 --> 38:02.071
that I already have
no feelings left at all for him.

38:04.365 --> 38:06.325
Today, I didn't even get angry with him.

38:09.954 --> 38:12.707
I was surprised by
how cunning my mind can be.

38:16.252 --> 38:18.587
Good morning.

38:18.671 --> 38:20.631
Jeong-in's sister is pregnant.

38:22.216 --> 38:24.468
Look, it says...

38:24.969 --> 38:26.095
What are you guys reading?

38:27.096 --> 38:29.015
- Hey.
- Congratulations. You're an aunt now.

38:36.314 --> 38:37.315
Jeong-in.

38:38.607 --> 38:39.650
Hello!

38:40.234 --> 38:41.110
Did she not know about it?

38:42.111 --> 38:44.613
I'm sure she knew.
She and her sister are like best friends.

38:46.073 --> 38:47.533
But she seems so surprised.

38:51.287 --> 38:53.039
- Hi.
- Hi.

38:54.832 --> 38:57.251
- Did you read the article?
- What article?

38:58.169 --> 39:00.046
Lee Seo-in is Jeong-in's sister, right?

39:00.504 --> 39:01.881
She quit her job because she's pregnant.

39:02.757 --> 39:04.633
- Really?
- I guess you didn't know.

39:05.509 --> 39:08.679
Her family will be over the moon
when Jeong-in gets married on top of that.

39:10.890 --> 39:12.099
Are you happy just hearing it?

39:13.184 --> 39:14.143
Yes, I am.

39:15.144 --> 39:17.188
I know exactly what you'll turn into.

39:17.438 --> 39:19.231
An extremely devoted husband.

39:41.754 --> 39:43.422
A colleague of mine just told me.

39:44.006 --> 39:45.341
Gi-seok proposed to her.

39:46.008 --> 39:47.093
Are you sure?

39:48.511 --> 39:52.556
Well...
Initially, I didn't believe it at all.

39:53.849 --> 39:58.354
But Gi-seok is smiling from ear to ear,

39:59.814 --> 40:04.068
almost as if he's getting married
the day after tomorrow or something.

40:09.031 --> 40:12.368
He must be bragging

40:13.994 --> 40:15.371
because it went well.

40:17.456 --> 40:18.624
Wait, so what does this mean?

40:19.333 --> 40:20.543
Is she dumping you, then?

40:22.086 --> 40:23.212
Let's talk later.

40:23.879 --> 40:24.922
Hey.

40:35.391 --> 40:36.392
Mr. Yu.

40:37.017 --> 40:38.310
What? Yes.

40:39.395 --> 40:41.689
- Are you feeling sick?
- No.

41:00.249 --> 41:04.211
There are too many overlaps
in the part about the review process.

41:05.129 --> 41:06.422
See the check marks?

41:07.047 --> 41:08.507
Revise these parts.

41:09.800 --> 41:12.970
And overall, it's too long.
It'll take up the entire meeting.

41:13.596 --> 41:14.763
I'll fix it.

41:19.602 --> 41:22.771
Hey, did you pass on the news to Ji-ho?

41:24.106 --> 41:24.982
What do you mean?

41:36.118 --> 41:38.078
- Congratulations.
- Why didn't you tell us?

41:38.162 --> 41:41.499
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

41:41.582 --> 41:44.418
Thank you. Well, I'm not sure
if I should be saying that.

41:44.919 --> 41:47.505
- I'm so sad that you're leaving.
- I know, I'm sad, too.

41:47.588 --> 41:50.090
Breaking news. Dr. Nam's wife is pregnant.

41:50.549 --> 41:51.926
What will happen to him now?

41:52.009 --> 41:55.179
Who knows? Last time, his mother-in-law
looked as if she wanted to kill him.

41:55.262 --> 41:56.305
What's this now?

41:58.557 --> 41:59.683
Gosh, cut it out.

42:00.309 --> 42:01.352
Good morning.

42:01.810 --> 42:04.396
By the way, what do men do these days
when their wives are pregnant?

42:05.147 --> 42:07.691
I'm old now, so I don't even know
what I should be doing.

42:07.775 --> 42:09.610
Tell me.

42:09.693 --> 42:11.278
- Have a nice day.
- Thank you. You too.

42:11.362 --> 42:12.446
- Have a nice day.
- Bye.

42:18.035 --> 42:19.411
What's the matter with you?

42:20.621 --> 42:21.664
Nothing.

42:24.333 --> 42:26.460
Don't give me that.
Something's clearly bothering you.

42:34.510 --> 42:36.303
See? I told you.

42:38.514 --> 42:40.057
I don't think he's sick, though.

42:40.683 --> 42:43.269
- Then maybe it's heartache.
- What?

42:44.770 --> 42:46.647
You're too hard-hearted.

42:46.730 --> 42:47.773
What the...

43:12.214 --> 43:13.215
Hello?

43:14.258 --> 43:15.426
Can we meet?

43:18.304 --> 43:19.513
I don't care even if it's late.

43:20.431 --> 43:21.932
I'll go to wherever works best for you.

43:24.351 --> 43:25.436
What is this about?

43:26.103 --> 43:27.146
You already know.

43:31.233 --> 43:32.401
What do you want to do?

43:35.279 --> 43:37.072
I don't think I can meet today.

43:38.073 --> 43:39.241
I'll let you know.

43:40.659 --> 43:41.952
Don't tell me you're avoiding me.

43:48.751 --> 43:50.169
Sure, let's meet today.

43:51.962 --> 43:52.963
What is this?

43:53.797 --> 43:55.007
Is Si-hoon moving back in?

43:55.799 --> 43:56.925
No, it's mine.

43:57.885 --> 43:59.261
Gosh, I'm so sick of this.

44:00.971 --> 44:03.641
You won't try
to talk Seo-in out of it, right?

44:04.516 --> 44:05.893
She can't live with Si-hoon.

44:07.978 --> 44:10.522
Are you that excited about
your sister getting a divorce?

44:10.606 --> 44:11.607
You think I'm excited?

44:12.191 --> 44:16.070
Living with someone who has a completely
different mindset is no better than death.

44:18.447 --> 44:19.657
I'm going to get a divorce.

44:21.033 --> 44:22.618
I'm talking about Seo-in, not you.

44:22.868 --> 44:24.453
I've decided to divorce your dad.

44:25.996 --> 44:27.039
What?

44:29.500 --> 44:31.001
- Is Dad having an affair?
- Hey.

44:32.294 --> 44:33.504
Then what's the problem?

44:33.754 --> 44:36.507
You've been putting up with him
all these years. Why now?

44:37.007 --> 44:40.552
You said one shouldn't live with someone
who has a completely different mindset.

44:42.054 --> 44:44.181
Hey, get me another glass of water.
With ice cubes.

44:46.016 --> 44:48.018
- Is divorce the latest trend?
- Go get me some water!

44:51.480 --> 44:52.648
By the way, Mom...

44:53.941 --> 44:55.317
If you and Dad get a divorce,

44:56.402 --> 44:57.403
whom should I choose?

44:58.112 --> 44:59.863
Don't say such silly things!

45:05.619 --> 45:07.871
Whether Seo-in gets a divorce or I do,

45:08.163 --> 45:10.499
you and Jeong-in shouldn't say anything
for now.

45:11.250 --> 45:12.251
Okay?

45:13.377 --> 45:14.378
Yes, I heard you.

45:22.845 --> 45:25.806
The total number of freshmen
will continue to go down every year.

45:26.682 --> 45:28.058
So we'll utilize empty classrooms?

45:29.393 --> 45:33.439
Yes. I gathered some ideas
and came up with that solution to prepare

45:33.856 --> 45:35.482
for what may happen in the near future.

45:36.483 --> 45:39.903
I appreciate that you're still working
so hard when you'll be retiring soon.

45:41.530 --> 45:43.741
I'll go through this.
You should get back to your office.

45:43.907 --> 45:44.867
Okay.

45:45.284 --> 45:47.619
By the way,
I met up with Gi-seok the other day.

45:47.703 --> 45:48.620
Did he tell you?

45:52.624 --> 45:54.835
Why don't we let them get married
when they want to do it?

45:56.420 --> 45:57.713
Why are you changing your mind?

45:58.464 --> 46:00.549
Did Jeong-in irk you again in any way?

46:02.134 --> 46:03.802
You're hurting my feelings here.

46:06.180 --> 46:09.183
Have you ever seen me going back
on my word after making a decision?

46:09.266 --> 46:10.559
Did you think I was like that?

46:12.144 --> 46:13.604
Gosh, of course not.

46:15.272 --> 46:17.733
Then why are you talking such nonsense?

46:19.943 --> 46:21.612
All children are like that.

46:22.404 --> 46:24.198
Whenever they're told by their parents

46:24.281 --> 46:26.033
to do something, they do the opposite.

46:28.202 --> 46:30.037
If we keep pressuring them,

46:30.496 --> 46:33.916
they may decide to go against us.
I'm just worried. That's all.

46:36.877 --> 46:38.295
Right.

46:38.962 --> 46:41.632
Children are like that, indeed.

46:42.925 --> 46:44.426
I heard you'll be a grandfather soon.

46:44.927 --> 46:46.345
Just enjoy that for now.

46:48.889 --> 46:50.057
I have to head out now.

46:56.230 --> 46:58.232
Well, Mr. Kwon.

46:58.899 --> 47:02.277
Since it's been brought up anyway,
we should keep the momentum going.

47:03.195 --> 47:05.781
Pressuring them is no way to do that.

47:06.323 --> 47:08.075
Well, what I mean is...

47:08.534 --> 47:12.079
I'm just concerned that it may drag out
indefinitely if we leave it up to them.

47:12.621 --> 47:14.164
Then maybe they're not meant to be.

47:15.916 --> 47:17.626
Anyway, that's what I think,

47:18.085 --> 47:20.629
so you make your own judgment.
Take it easy.

47:56.540 --> 47:57.749
Are you super busy today?

48:31.867 --> 48:34.328
- One iced Americano, please.
- For here?

48:35.203 --> 48:36.121
Would that be all?

49:08.028 --> 49:10.030
Ji-ho found out about
Gi-seok proposing to you.

49:10.364 --> 49:11.740
Yeong-jae told me.

49:28.298 --> 49:30.092
Yeong-jae is mad at me for telling you.

49:32.344 --> 49:33.679
- What?
- Talk to her.

49:35.347 --> 49:38.266
Jeong-in, he doesn't want to talk to you
because he thinks you're obnoxious.

49:38.350 --> 49:40.018
No, I never said that. Yes.

49:41.019 --> 49:42.396
I can't get a hold of Ji-ho.

49:42.896 --> 49:44.982
Did he tell you that he's meeting up
with Gi-seok?

49:46.441 --> 49:50.070
Yes, I called him earlier to ask him
if he wants to grab dinner together.

49:50.779 --> 49:53.365
By any chance, did he tell you
where they're meeting?

49:54.908 --> 49:56.201
No, I didn't ask.

49:57.661 --> 49:59.830
Jeong-in, the thing is...

50:01.707 --> 50:03.542
It may not be my place to say this,

50:05.252 --> 50:08.046
but Ji-ho is such a tough cookie.

50:09.673 --> 50:10.757
Yeong-jae.

50:12.467 --> 50:16.388
I'm sorry. I'm not exactly sure
what you mean by that.

50:16.888 --> 50:19.099
I'm sure you've figured out
this much about Ji-ho by now,

50:20.142 --> 50:23.895
but you can definitely trust him.
He'll never let you down.

50:24.104 --> 50:28.650
He has such a strong sense
of responsibility.

50:28.900 --> 50:30.694
I get what you're trying to say.

50:31.319 --> 50:32.487
That was random, wasn't it?

50:33.864 --> 50:36.908
I guess I wanted to brag about my buddy.

50:37.826 --> 50:38.952
That was sweet of you.

50:39.911 --> 50:41.038
I'll remember that.

50:45.125 --> 50:47.127
Your cappuccino is ready.

50:56.094 --> 50:59.389
Hyeon-su that blabbermouth
probably told you what happened.

51:00.015 --> 51:01.641
What more do you want to know?

51:07.022 --> 51:09.649
How much more
will you make it hard for Jeong-in?

51:12.444 --> 51:13.653
You're an obnoxious prick.

51:14.404 --> 51:15.447
Shall I provoke you more?

51:17.074 --> 51:19.493
Including Jeong-in's and my parents,

51:20.494 --> 51:23.121
I plan on telling everyone around us.

51:25.957 --> 51:27.584
You're one gutsy guy.

51:29.503 --> 51:31.088
And you're too much of a coward.

51:32.672 --> 51:33.924
What do you even know about me?

51:34.424 --> 51:36.009
I know this one thing for sure.

51:37.344 --> 51:38.804
You're doing this

51:39.846 --> 51:42.307
not because you want Jeong-in,
but because you can't lose to me.

51:43.934 --> 51:45.310
What do you gain from beating me?

51:47.521 --> 51:48.688
Like you said,

51:50.565 --> 51:53.026
I'm a mediocre man who's nothing special.

51:54.319 --> 51:58.156
And that's why you're the first to know
that I plan on telling our families.

52:00.200 --> 52:04.788
Wouldn't you be embarrassed that you tried
to compete against me?

52:07.916 --> 52:11.461
You seem to firmly believe that
her family will accept you with open arms.

52:12.754 --> 52:15.132
Doesn't the fact that
Jeong-in accepted me matter more?

52:18.176 --> 52:19.261
Gi-seok.

52:22.305 --> 52:25.767
Don't think of this as a word of advice
from some mediocre dude.

52:26.643 --> 52:30.939
Keeping this up will make both
of us look childish.

52:32.899 --> 52:33.942
Just stop it already.

52:37.571 --> 52:38.697
I will when you do.

52:41.616 --> 52:43.952
Why tell me to do something
that you can't do yourself?

52:45.912 --> 52:49.166
You plan on telling her parents? Go ahead.

52:50.750 --> 52:53.211
I can just picture
the embarrassment that awaits you,

52:54.880 --> 52:56.464
but I'm excited at the same time.

53:03.138 --> 53:04.472
I'll give up, then.

53:05.182 --> 53:06.141
What?

53:08.393 --> 53:09.853
You're giving up too easily.

53:12.230 --> 53:13.064
I'm giving up on you.

53:16.985 --> 53:19.946
I came here thinking I'd stop trying
if I couldn't get through to you today.

53:21.489 --> 53:23.450
I've been trying to be respectful,

53:25.619 --> 53:26.870
but I won't anymore.

53:28.330 --> 53:32.042
I'm done being considerate to you.

53:45.764 --> 53:48.266
I said, you can go when you hear him
coming up the stairs.

53:49.309 --> 53:51.811
What's taking him so long?
What if they actually fight this time?

53:52.437 --> 53:55.982
You must be thrilled
that two men are fighting over you.

53:58.318 --> 54:00.904
What did I say?
I told you not to get caught.

54:01.696 --> 54:04.199
I had no idea
that egotistical guy would do this.

54:05.700 --> 54:07.369
To Gi-seok, this is love.

54:09.746 --> 54:10.705
Jeez.

54:12.832 --> 54:15.835
Hey, do you know
what's even more ridiculous?

54:17.170 --> 54:20.382
In others' eyes,
Gi-seok is the victim no matter what.

54:20.799 --> 54:22.717
Everyone will feel so bad for him.

54:23.093 --> 54:24.803
Yes, I'm such a bitch.

54:25.262 --> 54:27.347
I mean, after saying he wants to...

54:28.390 --> 54:29.266
That must be him.

54:30.475 --> 54:31.476
Are you sure?

54:32.310 --> 54:34.396
I did hear someone walking up the stairs.

54:35.230 --> 54:36.314
What should I say to him?

54:36.690 --> 54:38.858
Nothing. Just apologize to him.

54:40.568 --> 54:41.945
Do I really owe him an apology?

54:43.113 --> 54:45.323
Are you becoming like Gi-seok?
Why can't you say sorry?

54:45.448 --> 54:48.535
Hey, I've said sorry to Ji-ho
so many times.

54:48.743 --> 54:51.913
That's because you're such a troublemaker.
Ji-ho is so understanding.

54:53.707 --> 54:55.959
- Aren't you leaving?
- Oh, I'm off.

54:56.042 --> 54:57.294
- All right.
- Hey.

54:57.627 --> 55:00.005
I'm going to sleep here
if he slams the door in my face!

55:00.839 --> 55:03.550
- Is my place your private motel?
- Yes, it is. Didn't you know?

55:03.800 --> 55:05.969
- Gosh, you kill me.
- I'll call you!

55:38.126 --> 55:39.461
I'm taking a shower now.

55:44.090 --> 55:45.216
What are you thinking?

55:49.304 --> 55:50.930
Will you keep talking with no clothes on?

55:53.099 --> 55:54.351
Just give me ten seconds.

56:02.233 --> 56:03.443
Jeong-in, seriously.

56:32.097 --> 56:33.640
I'll let go if you're not mad at me.

56:33.848 --> 56:35.600
If you're mad at me,
we can talk like this.

56:37.560 --> 56:38.728
What did you do wrong?

56:40.772 --> 56:41.815
I didn't tell you.

56:44.150 --> 56:46.403
I met up with Gi-seok without telling you.

56:48.363 --> 56:49.197
That's true.

56:49.948 --> 56:51.282
So I'm not the only one at fault.

56:55.829 --> 56:57.664
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

57:02.293 --> 57:03.336
Do you want some coffee?

57:04.587 --> 57:06.631
I had some beer at Yeong-ju's.

57:15.390 --> 57:18.143
- What about you?
- I need to drive you home.

57:19.310 --> 57:20.478
I'm going to sleep here.

57:24.274 --> 57:26.109
What? Can't I do that?

57:28.862 --> 57:30.822
Well, it's not that you can't.

57:31.281 --> 57:32.407
Then what?

57:36.286 --> 57:38.496
I bet you'll faint if I really sleep here.

57:38.830 --> 57:40.123
I'll be sleeping at Yeong-ju's.

58:09.736 --> 58:11.237
You're here to apologize, so go ahead.

58:15.366 --> 58:16.409
I'm sorry.

58:17.994 --> 58:21.498
I should've said that first,
but I kept beating around the bush.

58:27.170 --> 58:29.047
I accepted the ring he gave me.

58:30.757 --> 58:32.258
This will sound like an excuse,

58:33.384 --> 58:34.928
but I had no choice.

58:38.473 --> 58:39.807
To be really honest with you,

58:41.643 --> 58:43.102
I don't deserve to throw it at him

58:44.020 --> 58:45.522
or chuck it away.

58:47.190 --> 58:51.110
When it comes to that failed relationship,
I am the culprit.

58:56.824 --> 58:58.326
It couldn't have been an easy decision.

58:59.285 --> 59:00.495
You must've agonized over it.

59:03.498 --> 59:05.041
I learned it from you.

59:06.501 --> 59:08.503
Unlike you,
I'm not such a wonderful person.

59:10.213 --> 59:11.339
A while ago,

59:12.632 --> 59:14.384
when you told me about Eun-u's mom,

59:16.010 --> 59:17.679
I beat myself up a lot.

59:21.808 --> 59:23.893
It made me realize
that all the whining I was doing

59:26.312 --> 59:28.731
was extremely selfish and inconsiderate.

59:31.317 --> 59:32.735
Without you, I would've never known.

59:41.327 --> 59:42.370
From now on,

59:43.788 --> 59:45.540
I'm going to try to become like you.

59:49.002 --> 59:51.337
Are you teary-eyed now
because you don't want that?

01:00:02.140 --> 01:00:02.974
Gosh.

01:00:03.516 --> 01:00:04.976
You're still such a fool.

01:00:25.913 --> 01:00:27.123
I'm making myself some coffee.

01:00:34.881 --> 01:00:36.049
Where does Ji-ho live?

01:00:36.966 --> 01:00:37.967
Why?

01:00:38.468 --> 01:00:40.511
My sister just said
she isn't coming home tonight.

01:00:41.304 --> 01:00:43.473
She said she's at Yeong-ju's place,
but I don't buy it.

01:00:44.474 --> 01:00:46.267
So will you go to his place
and drag her out?

01:00:46.684 --> 01:00:48.394
No way. This is such a great opportunity.

01:00:48.936 --> 01:00:50.438
Doesn't Yeong-ju live in his building?

01:00:51.064 --> 01:00:52.982
I'll go see if she's there or not

01:00:53.066 --> 01:00:55.401
and use it to make her
give me an allowance.

01:00:55.985 --> 01:00:57.528
- Jae-in.
- What?

01:00:58.279 --> 01:00:59.530
You're such a bully.

01:01:00.531 --> 01:01:02.533
It's always the beggars
who care about their dignity.

01:01:03.826 --> 01:01:05.328
Anyway, what's Ji-ho's unit number?

01:01:08.164 --> 01:01:09.666
Are you trying to be loyal?

01:02:09.308 --> 01:02:11.018
Can you do something about that photo?

01:03:15.708 --> 01:03:17.710
Most people won't approve
of your relationship.

01:03:17.794 --> 01:03:21.255
In others' eyes, you're just someone
who cheated on her decent boyfriend.

01:03:21.339 --> 01:03:23.466
Everyone will badmouth you.

01:03:23.549 --> 01:03:26.177
Even if people talk shit about me,
I won't regret meeting Ji-ho.

01:03:26.260 --> 01:03:28.095
I held myself back because of you.

01:03:28.179 --> 01:03:29.555
Did we commit a crime or what?

01:03:29.639 --> 01:03:31.974
I'll tell them everything.
He can't keep doing this.

01:03:32.058 --> 01:03:35.102
Jeong-in said there's a guy she likes.

01:03:35.186 --> 01:03:36.187
Tell her I'd meet him.

01:03:36.270 --> 01:03:37.688
Tell Ji-ho this.

01:03:37.772 --> 01:03:40.149
He has to stay by her side
no matter what anyone says.

01:03:40.233 --> 01:03:42.276
He mustn't let her go
even if they have to elope.

01:03:42.360 --> 01:03:43.361
Do whatever you want.

01:03:43.444 --> 01:03:44.904
Ask me to meet up and visit me.

01:03:44.987 --> 01:03:46.280
I'll put up with anything.

01:03:46.364 --> 01:03:48.407
I'll think that I'm paying
for hurting you,

01:03:48.491 --> 01:03:50.743
so bug me all you want.
But don't bother Ji-ho.

01:03:50.827 --> 01:03:52.912
If you do, I'll do anything to stop you.

01:03:52.995 --> 01:03:54.539
It's nice to cry sometimes.

01:03:54.622 --> 01:03:55.957
I get to see you at this hour.

01:03:56.040 --> 01:03:58.751
- By the way, what is this place?
- Where people kiss secretly.
